  "body": "Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Create an empty folder\r\n2. `cd` into that folder and run `forge init`\r\n3. Resulting repo has two commits: `chore: forge init` followed by `forge install: ds-test`, as well as an untracked `foundry.toml` file\r\n\r\nI think it'd be preferable to have the `foundry.toml` file committed by default",
